Female Corporate In-House Recruiter – UAE Experience Essential
–
Abu Dhabi, Abu Dhabi, United Arab Emirates
Job Description
Responsibilities
Managing the recruitment process from headhunting, advertising, sourcing candidates and on-boarding.
Skills & Experience
Minimum of 3 years volume recruitment in the Gulf region working with blue collar employees.
Previous experience of working in a fast paced agency would be an advantage
Ability to communicate with employees at all levels.
Excellent knowledge of UAE labour regulations and laws.
Previous experience of working with recruitment agencies in labour source markets.
Fluency in English is essential.
Education
Degree holder
